metadata.name: The Artist
metadata.description:
10 unique, cool and diverse art luminaries on the Blockchain.

A community celebrating representation, inclusivity, and equal opportunities for all people in the art world. First-of-its-kind collection, featuring unique artworks representing a matrix of artworks + unique jigsaw puzzles.

Created by ART X PUZZLES (@artxpuzzles) 

Each sale supporting Artist Charity Choices to continue ART X PUZZLES global mission for Artist Charity Choices.
